 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">narrative violation!</a>=E2=
=80=9D or =E2=80=9C=E2=80=98<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
com/click/29363474.276514/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2Fyd=
