 solid; background-color: #ccc;">O.K., what=E2=80=99s the opposite of what =
you=E2=80=99re saying</a>, let=E2=80=99s try that=E2=80=9D? Well, I don=E2=
=80=99t, but what unicorns have I founded? Maybe the best founders want to =
challenge themselves by surrounding themselves with the VCs who are most an=
noying on Twitter.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/29363474.276514/aHR0cHM6Ly9tb2JpbGUudHdpdHRlci5jb20vbWF0dF9s=
